column5: Havent seen any reports in last week or so. Is that because trout is open now and nobody bother fishing for them anymore, or they stopped biting. I plan on going this weekend, we`ll see how it turns out.
It's your turn, Marko. Please post your report when you get back.
Will do. Have to try to get some points for my team this weekend.
When are you going?  Been meaning to check out the shorefishing by Fishmasters.
I was thier friday, the bite is still hot.
BRING BIG BIG BAGS CAUSE IT LOOKS LIKE 3-4 DAYS OF RAIN
I plan on going sunday early morning. Good to hear that teh bite is still hot, hopefully i`ll hook into some. Thank you
